longBusinessSummary: Arkanova Energy Corporation, a junior oil and gas producing company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of oil and gas properties in the United States. The company holds property interests in two counties in the State of Montana. It also holds leasehold interests located in Pondera and Glacier counties, Montana. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Austin, Texas.
